{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Yentsen Liu","description":"Gatsby starter for bootstrap a blog","url":"https://yentsenliu.com","author":"Yentsen Liu","twitter":"jaxx2104","adsense":""}},"post":{"id":"29e9a96f-b8ab-5175-85d0-64efd63ed015","html":"<figcaption>Johannes Gutenberg</figcaption>\n<p>The research will be an attempt to explore the potential of user interface and human centered design for sustaining a consolidated democratic future. Taking the feasible scale of a master’s thesis into account, the exploration is narrowed down to a core question: How to design interactive argument diagram for democratic communication?</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>The world is currently suffering a decline of democracy. User interface and experience have an unevenly important impact on this ongoing crisis. The digital democratic communication is truly one of the most prominent types of practice which has a great diversity within, whereas filter bubble has also become a trendy word describing the ubiquitous silos created by groups of like-minded people online. </p>\n<p>The research will be an attempt to explore the potential of user interface and human centered design for sustaining a consolidated democratic future. Taking the feasible scale of a master’s thesis into account, the exploration is narrowed down to a core question: How to design interactive argument diagram for democratic communication?</p>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 128.91246684350133%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Early Printing Press\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/Printing-press-9ec265253f068855f00558a9be7f3e03-245fd.png\" srcset=\"/static/Printing-press-9ec265253f068855f00558a9be7f3e03-7aee9.png 188w,\n/static/Printing-press-9ec265253f068855f00558a9be7f3e03-2014b.png 375w,\n/static/Printing-press-9ec265253f068855f00558a9be7f3e03-245fd.png 750w,\n/static/Printing-press-9ec265253f068855f00558a9be7f3e03-21a9b.png 754w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Two examples of interactive argument diagram:  Kialo (left) and Pol.is (right)</figcaption>\n<p>The overall methodology is a mixture of research through and for design. The research process will comprise the following activities: interview, case study, quantitative research, and co-creation. </p>\n<p>The expected outcomes of this research are listed below:</p>\n<p>A series of test that carries out the pros and cons of existing systems of argument diagramming\nA novel design of argument diagramming for a better democratic outcome\nAn exploration on how to involve behavior tracking technique and quantitative analysis in human-centered design research and in experimental political sciences\nA theoretical exploration on what democratic value of design should be and how to operationalize it in an empirical and constructive design research</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.43356643356644%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Movable metal type, and composing stick, descended from Gutenberg's press. Photo by Willi Heidelbach. Licensed under CC BY 2.5\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-df60d.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-45144.jpg 188w,\n/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-2f941.jpg 375w,\n/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-df60d.jpg 750w,\n/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-b1889.jpg 1125w,\n/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-1d6f8.jpg 1500w,\n/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-a84b6.jpg 2250w,\n/static/movable-type-0d1540b9a8fca9db753ad10ae0a3427e-85da8.jpg 2288w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p><em>Movable metal type, and composing stick, descended from Gutenberg’s press. Photo by Willi Heidelbach. Licensed under CC BY 2.5</em></p>\n<figure>\n\t<blockquote>\n\t\t<p>It is a press, certainly, but a press from which shall flow in inexhaustible streams… Through it, god will spread his word.</p>\n\t\t<footer>\n\t\t\t<cite>—Johannes Gutenberg</cite>\n\t\t</footer>\n\t</blockquote>\n</figure>","frontmatter":{"layout":"post","title":"Designing Diagram for Democracy","path":"/master-thesis-plan/","category":"thesis","tags":["Digital Democracy","Computing Democracy","User Interface","Exmperimental Political Science"],"description":"How to design interactive argument diagram for democratic communication? This is Yentsen Liu's ongoing master's thesis work at Aalto University, Finland.","date":"2018/10/19","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":500,"height":357,"src":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-7f380.jpg","srcSet":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-7f380.jpg 1x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-b4bc2.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-ac12b.jpg 2x","srcWebp":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-e6ca4.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-e6ca4.webp 1x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-4bf37.webp 1.5x,\n/static/thesis-f70e83a174966c387c0479697cc02b11-0c5e8.webp 2x"}}}}}},"pageContext":{}}